.vice.com/en/article/fable-developer-responds-to-backlash-over-too-easy-difficulty/"&gt;《寓言开发者回应“太简单”难度的强烈反对》&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com"&gt;VICE&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 14:25:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.vice.com/en/article/fable-developer-responds-to-backlash-over-too-easy-difficulty/</guid></item><item><title>《办公室》、《主播》和《南方公园》都将笑话隐藏在几乎没有人会看到的地方</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/article/the-office-anchorman-and-south-park-all-hid-jokes-where-almost-nobody-would-see-them/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;喜剧倾向于将笑话放在前面和中心，以便轻松获得创作者所希望的笑声。从表面上看，以其他方式做事似乎会适得其反。但是，话又说回来，谁不喜欢听他们在前几次错过的笑话[…]&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.vice.com/en/article/the-office-anchorman-and-south-park-all-hid-jokes-where-almost-nobody-would-see-them/"&gt;《办公室》、《主持人》和《南方公园》都将笑话隐藏在几乎没有人会看到的地方，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com"&gt;VICE&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 14:20:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.vice.com/en/article/the-office-anchorman-and-south-park-all-hid-jokes-where-almost-nobody-would-see-them/</guid></item><item><title>《办公室》片场非常寒冷，因为史蒂夫·卡瑞尔因这种健康状况而无法停止出汗</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/article/the-office-set-was-freezing-cold-because-steve-carell-couldnt-stop-sweating-due-to-this-medical-condition/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;《办公室》是深受人们喜爱的现代情景喜剧之一，许多人都转向观看“舒适观看”。具有讽刺意味的是，演员们在拍摄该剧时一点也不舒服——至少在九季中的前七季是这样。你看，《办公室》的布景在制作过程中异常寒冷，并且 […]&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.vice.com/en/article/the-office-set-was-freezing-cold-because-steve-carell-couldnt-stop-sweating-due-to-this-medical-condition/"&gt;史蒂夫·卡瑞尔因这种健康状况而无法停止出汗，“办公室”场景非常寒冷，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com"&gt;VICE&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 14:15:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.vice.com/en/article/the-office-set-was-freezing-cold-because-steve-carell-couldnt-stop-sweating-due-to-this-medica